high_descs: Turn around then turn right and head to the island counter and turn to the right
Pick up the apple from the island counter
Turn left and then turn left and go to the microwave
Microwave the apple and then take it out of the microwave
Turn left and go past the island counter then turn left and make your way to the fridge
Put the apple in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple into the fridge

high_descs: Turn to the left and face the island.
Pick up the apple from the center of the island.
Carry the apple and turn around.
Open the microwave and place the apple inside. Shut the door, then open it again. Take out the apple.
Hold the apple and turn to the left and then the right to locate the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple inside. Shut the door.
Move to the end of the kitchen island, so your back is to the counter with the toaster and the coffee maker is straight across the room.
Pick up the apple from the island.
Turn to face the microwave on the counter behind you.
Place the apple in the microwave and remove once heated.
Carry the apple around the island to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the apple on the third shelf next to the bowl.
